preference.name: PCA_VariantRule_SavedQueries
preference.preference_description: Lists the saved queries displayed in the client for Variant Rules in the Load Configuration dialog of Variant Configuration View. The only value available by default is "Variant Rules", which is a generic saved query given to perform search on Variant Rules. Additional Valid Values: the names of saved queries created on a specific type of rule.
